IN DOM :all the elements are called as objects.
property:
the values that we can set to the objects
(like changing content of an html element)
method(Action). (like adding or the deleting)


Method of document object:
getting element: 
1) getting element by id
2)getting element by class
3)getting element by tagname
4)getting element by selector


<!DOCTYPE html>
